			<div class="excerpt-container"><div class="excerpt"><em>The following is from Morris Collins's </em>The Tavern at the End of History<em>. Collins is also the author of </em>Horse Latitudes<em> (Dzanc). His work has been awarded an O. Henry Prize and a Massachusetts Cultural Council Fellowship, He lives in Boston and teaches at The College of the Holy Cross.</em></div></div>
